      "acceptanceCriteria": "Version-controlled solver with documented regression test suite; ANSYS Fluent 2022R2 with FDA-acknowledged validation history.",
      "rationale": "ANSYS Fluent 2022R2 is used under a documented software quality plan. Version control, change logs, and a regression test suite covering blood-analog fluid benchmarks are maintained. SQA level meets MRL 2 requirements."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
