      "rationale": "CFD-predicted normalized index of hemolysis (NIH) values agree with experimental measurements within 12% across all five flow-speed operating points. Relative hemolysis index RH ranges from 0.71 to 0.94, satisfying the RH < 1 acceptance criterion at all conditions."
