      "rationale": "The primary QoI, normalized index of hemolysis, is the accepted metric for blood trauma assessment per ASTM F1841 and FDA guidance. The relative hemolysis index RH provides a direct comparison to the predicate device, ensuring clinical relevance of model outputs."
